CustomField.description: This field updates the Audit / Approval Policy on child processes overriding any existing policy. If left unchecked, the policy propagates until a different policy is detected.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field updates the Audit / Approval Policy on child processes overriding any existing policy. If left unchecked, the policy propagates until a different policy is detected.
CustomField.label: Update Child Process Policies
